        <summary type="html">A friend recently asked me if I am a results or a process person. I told her that I‚Äôm a momentum person. I like to move. I don‚Äôt like breaks. But when we hit the one year mark of Virtual Coffee, and I realized that I hadn‚Äôt had a week off in a year I didn‚Äôt want to take time off, but I thought I probably should. And it was the right call.</summary>
      

      
      
